{"tid":463704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"農夫演唱會 9/11 請好好珍惜農夫","createTime":"2017-11-09T17:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T10:10:42.000Z","uid":12243,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee2c121a89e96b94af5a2a155dbd94621f81c338","tid":463704,"uid":12243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:59:25.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完農夫演唱會 真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全晚幾乎都係唱返以前d舊歌 <br />\n重新找到你 偉大航道 456Wing等等<br />\n淨係個前奏一出d回憶已經返曬尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外佢地事隔咁多年咁難得開返演唱會<br />\n明明可以等自己唱多d歌 <br />\n都特登邀請左咁多香港嘅其他rapper尼表演 <br />\n寧願自己少d時間唱都咁落力推廣rap文化 當然仲未計dancer同其他嘉賓...<br />\n証明佢地真係好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可惜之後嘅場都無時間去睇 下一次開又唔知係幾時了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有好多歌未聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8465a48b8c14a91433bbea12420e06241ff24612","tid":463704,"uid":12243,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T18:07:30.000Z","msg":"完show仲要逐個送客送到全部走曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bfe06c38659071ddb61f48b85d685a5fd689e5","tid":463704,"uid":22270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T21:32:50.000Z","msg":"上一次開比人cancel再補返場<br />\n開一場都坐唔滿<br />\n今次坐到咁爆<br />\n希望大家真係欣賞唔好晒左張飛"},{"pid":"bacfe79982b8d87633a458b48840eb22ba6edbfc","tid":463704,"uid":50881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:05:51.000Z","msg":"開場個暖場都好sweet<br />\n真係無諗過可以咁近同佢地傾計<br />\n成件事好warm"},{"pid":"01b3ef1effd6624d0cfff3706c63229d5e9cf13d","tid":463704,"uid":47,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"全場一齊唱456wing就睇得出佢地好感動<img src=\"/asse